      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Mar 2025 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国私营部门在10个月内以最快的速度扩展</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/germany-private-sector-expands-at-fastest-pace-in-10-months</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国的私营部门在10个月内以最快的速度增长，希望政府支出的大量增加将超过美国关税的任何打击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/germany-private-sector-expands-at-fastest-pace-in-10-months</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Mar 2025 08:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
