      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/french-business-activity-recovers-more-than-thought-on-factories</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国的私营部门业务活动的收缩少于预期，制造业的上升无法抵消持续的政治不确定性。]]></description>
